# Single source of truth for launchd automation agents.
# Format (pipe-delimited):
#   name|description|in_default_profile|friendly_alias
# - name:               canonical agent name (matches launchd/com.user.<name>.plist)
# - description:        human-readable summary shown in list/install output
# - in_default_profile: yes|no — whether enabled when DOTFILES_PROFILE_AUTOMATIONS is unset
# - friendly_alias:     short name accepted by setup-automation.sh (optional)
#
# Lines starting with # and blank lines are ignored.

dotfiles-backup|Automated daily backups|yes|backup
dotfiles-doctor|Daily health monitoring|yes|doctor
obsidian-sync|Obsidian vault synchronization|no|
repo-update|Repository updates|yes|
log-cleanup|Weekly log rotation|yes|
brew-audit|Weekly Brewfile drift detection|yes|
weekly-digest|Weekly automation health digest|yes|
lmstudio-server|LM Studio local server|no|lmstudio
spicetify-reapply|Re-apply spicetify on Spotify updates|yes|
